光？）我哋好醒嘅，明知藝人車牌咁易認，咁緊係唔好泊死一個位啦！如果真係要偷雞，就周圍泊下啦！」<br />\n<br />\n當黎諾懿得悉詩雅遭住戶指控，三年來為求貪方便霸佔訪客車位時，諾懿大感驚訝：「佢貪方便呀？咁唔好諗啦！係咪太多訪客呀？會唔會佢以為自己買咗訪客車位呀？三年都係咁泊？佢都Ok喎泊咗三年，等陣我問吓佢住邊區先，不過盡可能就唔好啦！要乖乖哋，所以我都要了解件事先。講真都係貪方便，不過算啦，大家原諒佢啦！咁靚嘅女仔。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210123/429767864216588288916732.jpeg/nkugv8kxr_dkyqW_JWS-_GsATQr_T1G2plo_ZZxaP2U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210123%2F429767864216588288916732.jpeg%2Fnkugv8kxr_dkyqW_JWS-_GsATQr_T1G2plo_ZZxaP2U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3b8ef75a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母la"},{"pid":"f9f4eef7c0374cca219636fcabe806012b4e14fb","tid":2377684,"uid":73972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:50:27.000Z","msg":"又唔係好笑，咁是非不分既野都講得出唔知佢點教仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0626c43f2a78efb474c0739c1faa136ef4323ac4","tid":2377684,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac551d1738625a1df5bf94d3099924d9c0e13745","tid":2377684,"uid":128369,"like":102,"dislike":7,"score":95,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T23:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"港府叫市民要寬恕，對港府同黑警做過既衰嘢當粉筆字抹走"},{"pid":"d44b78609ea4cf198bc0df32223ec867bbea28f4","tid":2377684,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"84b8ef2cfa7ff7821dca6f8e65c3af1ed35b0f89","tid":2377684,"uid":7828,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcRgRzd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcRgRzd.jpg&h=7c616500&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349a8dfcca5feb9dd1ff4fc3aad0764c167bae02","tid":2377684,"uid":13062